540001,117,391,2,16,1,99,13,"Tattha caran ti amma, mayaṃ tayopi janā bhātupariyesanaṃ carantā disodisaṃ gamissāmāti naṃ assāsesuṃ. "
540002,117,392,2,31,1,159,21,"Tato sudassano cintesi‘‘ sace tayopi ekaṃ disaṃ gamissāma, papañco bhavissati, tīhi tīṇi ṭhānāni gantuṃ vaṭṭati– ekena devalokaṃ, ekena himavantaṃ, ekena manussalokaṃ. "
540003,117,392,32,42,1,76,9,"Sace kho pana kāṇāriṭṭho manussalokaṃ gamissati, yattheva bhūridattaṃ passati. "
540004,117,392,43,63,1,92,16,"Taṃ gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā jhāpetvā essati, esa kakkhaḷo pharuso, na sakkā etaṃ tattha pesetun’’ ti. "
540005,117,392,64,93,1,154,22,"Cintetvā ca pana‘‘ tāta ariṭṭha, tvaṃ devalokaṃ gaccha, sace devatāhi dhammaṃ sotukāmāhi bhūridatto devalokaṃ nīto, tato naṃ ānehī’’ ti ariṭṭhaṃ devalokaṃ pahiṇi. "
540006,117,392,94,113,1,109,14,"Subhogaṃ pana‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ himavantaṃ gantvā pañcasu mahānadīsu bhūridattaṃ upadhāretvā ehī’’ ti himavantaṃ pahiṇi. "
