542817,117,2196,52,66,1,76,11,"Sace etena {yānenā}ti mahārāja, yassetaṃ evarūpaṃ yānaṃ sace atthi, etena yānena. "
542818,117,2196,67,108,1,242,35,"Samacariyā daḷhā {dhitī}ti yassa samacariyā ca dhiti ca daḷhā hoti thirā, so etena yānena yasmā esa ratho sabbakāmaduho rāja, yathādhippete sabbakāme deti, tasmā na jātu nirayaṃ vaje, ekaṃsenetaṃ dhārehi, evarūpena yānena nirayaṃ na gacchasīti attho. "
542819,117,2196,109,141,1,136,22,"Iti kho, mahārāja, yaṃ maṃ avaca‘‘ ācikkha me, nārada, suddhimaggaṃ, yathā ahaṃ no niraye pateyyan’’ ti, ayaṃ te so mayā anekapariyāyena akkhātoti. "
