542832,117,2210,2,7,1,20,2,[ 546]9. Vidhurajātakavaṇṇanā 
542833,117,2211,2,2,1,17,1,Catuposathakaṇḍaṃ 
542834,117,2212,2,16,1,91,11,Paṇḍu kisiyāsi {dubbalā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto attano paññāpāramiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
542835,117,2212,17,57,1,353,34,"Ekadivasañhi bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, satthā mahāpañño puthupañño gambhīrapañño javanapañño hāsapañño tikkhapañño nibbedhikapañño parappavādamaddano, attano paññānubhāvena khattiyapaṇḍitādīhi abhisaṅkhate sukhumapañhe bhinditvā te dametvā nibbisevane katvā tīsu saraṇesu ceva sīlesu ca patiṭṭhāpetvā amatagāmimaggaṃ paṭipādesī’’ ti. "
542836,117,2212,58,95,1,201,23,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ anacchariyaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ tathāgato paramābhisambodhippatto parappavādaṃ bhinditvā khattiyādayo dameyya. "
542837,117,2212,96,102,1,83,6,Purimabhavasmiñhi bodhiñāṇaṃ pariyesantopi tathāgato paññavā parappavādamaddanoyeva. 
542838,117,2212,103,130,1,224,25,Tathā hi ahaṃ vidhurakāle saṭṭhiyojanubbedhe kāḷapabbatamuddhani puṇṇakaṃ nāma yakkhasenāpatiṃ attano ñāṇabaleneva dametvā nibbisevanaṃ katvā pañcasīlesu patiṭṭhāpento attano jīvitaṃ dāpesin’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
542839,117,2213,2,10,1,75,8,Atīte kururaṭṭhe indapatthanagare dhanañcayakorabyo nāma rājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
542840,117,2213,11,17,1,58,6,Vidhurapaṇḍito nāma amacco tassa atthadhammānusāsako ahosi. 
542841,117,2213,18,43,1,260,24,So madhurakatho mahādhammakathiko sakalajambudīpe rājāno hatthikantavīṇāsarena paluddhahatthino viya attano madhuradhammadesanāya palobhetvā tesaṃ sakasakarajjāni gantuṃ adadamāno buddhalīlāya mahājanassa dhammaṃ desento mahantena yasena tasmiṃ nagare paṭivasi. 
542842,117,2214,2,39,1,349,35,Tadā hi bārāṇasiyampi gihisahāyakā cattāro brāhmaṇamahāsālā mahallakakāle kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā vanamūlaphalāhārā tattheva ciraṃ vasitvā loṇambilasevanatthāya cārikaṃ caramānā aṅgaraṭṭhe kālacampānagaraṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase bhikkhāya nagaraṃ pavisiṃsu. 
542843,117,2214,40,61,1,199,21,Tattha cattāro sahāyakā kuṭumbikā tesaṃ iriyāpathesu pasīditvā vanditvā bhikkhābhājanaṃ gahetvā ekekaṃ attano nivesane nisīdāpetvā paṇītena āhārena parivisitvā paṭiññaṃ gāhāpetvā uyyāneyeva vāsāpesuṃ. 
542844,117,2214,62,86,1,200,21,"Te cattāro tāpasā catunnaṃ kuṭumbikānaṃ gehesu nibaddhaṃ bhuñjitvā divāvihāratthāya eko tāpaso tāvatiṃsabhavanaṃ gacchati, eko nāgabhavanaṃ, eko supaṇṇabhavanaṃ, eko korabyarañño migājinauyyānaṃ gacchati. "
542845,117,2214,87,102,1,105,14,"Tesu yo devalokaṃ gantvā divāvihāraṃ karoti, so sakkassa yasaṃ oloketvā attano upaṭṭhākassa tameva vaṇṇeti. "
542846,117,2214,103,117,1,110,13,"Yo nāgabhavanaṃ gantvā divāvihāraṃ karoti, so nāgarājassa sampattiṃ oloketvā attano upaṭṭhākassa tameva vaṇṇeti. "
542847,117,2214,118,132,1,115,13,"Yo supaṇṇabhavanaṃ gantvā divāvihāraṃ karoti, so supaṇṇarājassa vibhūtiṃ oloketvā attano upaṭṭhākassa tameva vaṇṇeti. "
542848,117,2214,133,148,1,145,14,"Yo dhanañcayakorabyarājassa uyyānaṃ gantvā divāvihāraṃ karoti, so dhanañcayakorabyarañño sirisobhaggaṃ oloketvā attano upaṭṭhākassa tameva vaṇṇeti. "
542849,117,2215,2,31,1,219,27,"Te cattāropi janā taṃ tadeva ṭhānaṃ patthetvā dānādīni puññāni katvā āyupariyosāne eko sakko hutvā nibbatti, eko saputtadāro nāgabhavane nāgarājā hutvā nibbatti, eko supaṇṇabhavane simbalivimāne supaṇṇarājā hutvā nibbatti. "
542850,117,2215,32,37,1,58,5,Eko dhanañcayakorabyarañño aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbatti. 
542851,117,2215,38,45,1,62,7,Tepi tāpasā aparihīnajjhānā kālaṃ katvā brahmaloke nibbattiṃsu. 
542852,117,2215,46,56,1,91,10,Korabyakumāro vuḍḍhimanvāya pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhahitvā dhammena samena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
542853,117,2215,57,61,1,25,4,So pana jūtavittako ahosi. 
542854,117,2215,62,74,1,79,10,"So vidhurapaṇḍitassa ovāde ṭhatvā dānaṃ deti, sīlaṃ rakkhati, uposathaṃ upavasati. "
542855,117,2216,2,18,1,113,11,So ekadivasaṃ samādinnuposatho‘‘ vivekamanubrūhissāmī’’ ti uyyānaṃ gantvā manuññaṭṭhāne nisīditvā samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
542856,117,2216,19,38,1,138,15,Sakkopi samādinnuposatho‘‘ devaloke palibodho hotī’’ ti manussaloke tameva uyyānaṃ āgantvā ekasmiṃ manuññaṭṭhāne nisīditvā samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
542857,117,2216,39,56,1,130,12,Varuṇanāgarājāpi samādinnuposatho‘‘ nāgabhavane palibodho hotī’’ ti tatthevāgantvā ekasmiṃ manuññaṭṭhāne nisīditvā samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
542858,117,2216,57,73,1,130,12,Supaṇṇarājāpi samādinnuposatho‘‘ supaṇṇabhavane palibodho hotī’’ ti tatthevāgantvā ekasmiṃ manuññaṭṭhāne nisīditvā samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
542859,117,2216,74,93,1,218,19,Tepi cattāro janā sāyanhasamaye sakaṭṭhānehi nikkhamitvā maṅgalapokkharaṇitīre samāgantvā aññamaññaṃ oloketvā pubbasinehavasena samaggā sammodamānā hutvā aññamaññaṃ mettacittaṃ upaṭṭhapetvā madhurapaṭisanthāraṃ kariṃsu. 
542860,117,2216,94,105,1,83,10,"Tesu sakko maṅgalasilāpaṭṭe nisīdi, itarepi attano attano yuttāsanaṃ ñatvā nisīdiṃsu. "
542861,117,2216,106,125,1,78,13,"Atha ne sakko āha‘‘ mayaṃ cattāropi rājānova , amhesu pana kassa sīlaṃ mahantan’’ ti? "
542862,117,2216,126,142,1,83,12,Atha naṃ varuṇanāgarājā āha‘‘ tumhākaṃ tiṇṇaṃ janānaṃ sīlato mayhaṃ sīlaṃ mahantan’’ ti.
542863,117,2216,143,150,1,19,3,‘‘ Kimettha kāraṇan’’ ti?
542864,117,2216,151,184,1,234,27,"‘‘ Ayaṃ supaṇṇarājā amhākaṃ jātānampi ajātānampi paccāmittova, ahaṃ evarūpaṃ amhākaṃ jīvitakkhayakaraṃ paccāmittaṃ disvāpi kodhaṃ na karomi, iminā kāraṇena mama sīlaṃ mahantan’’ ti vatvā idaṃ dasakanipāte catuposathajātake paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha–"
542865,117,2217,2,14,1,57,10,"‘ ‘ Yo kopaneyye na karoti kopaṃ, na kujjhati sappuriso kadāci; "
542866,117,2218,2,25,1,60,10,"Kuddhopi so nāvikaroti kopaṃ, taṃ ve naraṃ samaṇamāhu loke’’ ti.( jā.1.10.24); "
542867,117,2219,2,8,1,32,5,Tattha {yo}ti khattiyādīsu yo koci. 
542868,117,2219,9,18,1,76,8,{Kopaneyye}ti kujjhitabbayuttake puggale khantīvādītāpaso viya kopaṃ na karoti. 
542869,117,2219,19,26,1,39,6,{Kadācī}ti yo kismiñci kāle na kujjhateva. 
542870,117,2219,27,42,1,98,13,"{Kuddhopī}ti sace pana so sappuriso kujjhati, atha kuddhopi taṃ kopaṃ nāvikaroti cūḷabodhitāpaso viya. "
542871,117,2219,43,61,1,89,14,Taṃ ve naran ti mahārājāno taṃ ve purisaṃ samitapāpatāya loke paṇḍitā‘‘ samaṇan’’ ti kathenti. 
542872,117,2219,62,73,1,54,9,"Ime pana guṇā mayi santi, tasmā mameva sīlaṃ mahantanti. "
542873,117,2220,2,34,1,189,26,"Taṃ sutvā supaṇṇarājā‘‘ ayaṃ nāgo mama aggabhakkho, yasmā panāhaṃ evarūpaṃ aggabhakkhaṃ disvāpi khudaṃ adhivāsetvā āhārahetu pāpaṃ na karomi, tasmā mameva sīlaṃ mahantan’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha–"
542874,117,2221,2,13,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Ūnūdaro yo sahate jighacchaṃ, danto tapassī mitapānabhojano; "
542875,117,2222,2,25,1,57,10,"Āhārahetu na karoti pāpaṃ, taṃ ve naraṃ samaṇamāhu loke’’ ti.( jā.1.10.25); "
