549950,118,163,54,68,1,79,12,"Saññāya yutto bhavo, saññāvataṃ vā bhavo, saññā vā ettha bhave atthīti saññābhavo. "
549951,118,163,69,79,1,91,10,So kāmabhavo ca asaññābhavamutto rūpabhavo ca nevasaññānāsaññābhavamutto arūpabhavo ca hoti. 
549952,118,164,2,8,1,44,5,"Na saññābhavo asaññābhavo, so rūpabhavekadeso. "
549953,118,164,9,21,1,117,10,"Oḷārikattābhāvato nevasaññā, sukhumattena sabbhāvato nāsaññāti nevasaññānāsaññā, tāya yutto bhavo nevasaññānāsaññābhavo. "
549954,118,164,22,37,1,124,14,"Atha vā oḷārikāya saññāya abhāvā sukhumāya ca bhāvā nevasaññānāsaññā asmiṃ bhaveti nevasaññānāsaññābhavo, so arūpabhavekadeso. "
549955,118,164,38,53,1,96,12,"Ekena rūpakkhandhena vokiṇṇo bhavo, eko vā vokāro, assa bhavassāti ekavokārabhavo, so asaññābhavova. "
549956,118,164,54,70,1,104,13,"Catūhi arūpakkhandhehi vokiṇṇo bhavo, cattāro vā vokārā assa bhavassāti catuvokārabhavo, so arūpabhavo eva. "
