549986,118,169,2,28,1,275,23,"Tena na kāye vedanānupassanā cittadhammānupassanā vā, atha kho kāyānupassanāyevāti kāyasaṅkhāte vatthusmiṃ kāyānupassanākārasseva dassanena asammissato vavatthānaṃ dassitaṃ hoti, tathā na kāye aṅgapaccaṅgavinimuttaekadhammānupassanā, nāpi kesalomādivinimuttaitthipurisānupassanā. "
